text: Blackjack is a 1998 Canadian American television action movie directed by John Woo and starring Dolph Lundgren, Peter Keleghan, Fred Williamson, Kate Vernon, Belle Perez, Andrew Jackson, Saul Rubinek, Kam Heskin. It was distributed by Miramax Films. ==Other websites== * Category:1998 action movies Category:Canadian action movies Category:American action movies Category:Television movies Category:Movies set in Toronto Category:Movies directed by John Woo
